# Guide to Gear - MDX Content Website

**Website**: www.guidetogear.com
**Description**: A comprehensive guide website for gear, equipment, and tools

This is a statically generated website using Next.js 15 with MDX content.

## Key Technologies
- Next.js 15 with App Router
- MDX for content (gray-matter, next-mdx-remote)
- Zod for schema validation
- Tailwind CSS for styling
- Static Site Generation (SSG)

## Content Structure
- MDX files in `/content` directory
- Frontmatter with title, description, date, tags
- Dynamic routes at `/[slug]` for each MDX file

## SEO Requirements
- All pages must have proper meta tags
- Use descriptive titles and descriptions
- Include Open Graph and Twitter Card meta tags
- Optimize for "guide to gear" related keywords
- Ensure proper heading hierarchy (H1, H2, H3)
- Add structured data where appropriate

## Development
- Add MDX files to `/content` directory
- Use proper frontmatter format with SEO-optimized titles/descriptions
- Pages are statically generated at build time
- Always include meta descriptions and relevant tags
